column5: ...and I renewed online last year on January 1st in the wee hours of the morning no less si I would be legit for the opener (nothing like waiting till the last minute)and have been fishing with a temporary card I printed off ever since.  I've also called twice for a new one!  Maybe one of those postal workers you're referring to are fishing with my card! lol Just kidding!
Did my wife's renewal online two weeks ago........................................Still waiting.  Kerry
Gotta agree with you on that one. Nobody has a more back breaking job then a postal worker  My card is good til dec 31 2010....so I'm set for awhile.
Same great service for me...amazing!!! Ted
I did my renewal on the net on the week-end.   Came in today.
Me and my dad renewed online, got it in 2 days. Makes you think.
